[size=5][b]‚ú® What is Big Willy Mod?[/b][/size]

Big Willy Mod is an [b]officially endorsed mod[/b] featuring [b]BigWilly[/b] (@Its.BigWilly)! 

[b]Developed in collaboration with BigWilly himself[/b], this mod was designed with direct input from Willy himself. BigWilly & fans participated in the design and development process, ensuring his in-game representation authentically captures his personality and role in the community.

[size=5][b]üéÆ Key Features[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][b]BigWilly as an NPC[/b]: BigWilly brought to life as a fully-featured character with his real character's appearance, daily schedule, and personality
[*][b]"Spread the Word" Quest[/b]: Help BigWilly promote the "Stay Silly" lifestyle by tagging graffiti spots around Hyland Point
[*][b]Stay Silly Cap Reward[/b]: Earn the exclusive "Stay Silly Cap" - inspired by BigWilly's real merch brand (staysilly.shop)
[*][b]Dynamic Dialogue[/b]: Context-aware conversations with BigWilly's signature "Stay Silly, brother!" catchphrase
[*][b]Customer Integration[/b]: BigWilly acts as a customer with unique spending habits, drug preferences, and relationship mechanics
[*][b]Text Message Updates[/b]: Receive progress updates via text messages as you complete quest objectives - just like his community updates!
[/list]

[b]Daily Schedule:[/b]
[list]
[*][b]7:00 AM[/b]: Starts his day at the sewers
[*][b]9:00 AM[/b]: Walks to the pawnshop exterior
[*][b]9:30 AM - 1:30 PM[/b]: Hangs out at the pawnshop (4 hours)
[*][b]1:30 PM[/b]: Heads to the arcade
[*][b]2:00 PM - 4:00 PM[/b]: Spends time at the arcade (2 hours)
[*][b]4:30 PM - 11:00 PM[/b]: Gambles at slot machines in the casino ($10 per spin)
[*][b]11:00 PM[/b]: Returns to the sewer vents for the night
[/list]

[size=5][b]üì¶ Installation[/b][/size]

[list=1]
[*]Install the latest version of [b]S1API (Forked)[/b]
[*]Download the latest [b]BigWillyMod.dll[/b] from the Files section
[*]Place it in your game's [font=Courier New]Mods[/font] folder
[*]Launch the game - Big Willy will spawn automatically!
[/list]

[size=5][b]üéÆ How to Play[/b][/size]

[list=1]
[*]Launch the game and load your save (or start a new game)
[*]Find Big Willy following his daily schedule (check the locations above)
[*]Talk to Big Willy to start the "Spread the Word" quest
[*]Follow the quest markers to graffiti spots around town
[*]Tag the required number of spots with spray paint
[*]Return to Big Willy to complete the quest and claim your Stay Silly Cap!
[/list]

[b]Console Commands (Optional):[/b]
[code]give stay_silly_cap 1    # Spawn the Stay Silly Cap directly in your inventory[/code]

[size=5][b]üêõ Known Issues[/b][/size]

[list]
[*]The Graffiti Quest requires at least one untagged graffiti surface to start. If all surfaces are tagged, Big Willy will offer the hat directly without a quest
[*]If you start the quest and are somehow soft locked in it through other means, the quest can still be completed by returning to Big Willy
[/list]

